Package: MethXY
Title: Sex Chromosome Analysis for DNA Methylation Arrays
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Chao", "Wang", , "cwang9973@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools for analyzing sex chromosomes 
    using DNA methylation array data. 
    It offers functions for data preprocessing, quality control, 
    and statistical analysis tailored to 
    the unique features of X and Y chromosomes.
